testext, a Nose plugin for running tests in C extensions

The plugin and test running helper:

testext/
	setup.py
	testext/
		# The main plugin. runner is a console program that runs a named test,
		# plugin is the nose plugin
		plugin.py
		runner.py
	_testext/
		An extension needed by the test runner to dlopen and dlsym the test:
		testext.c
		test_testext.c

